      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in absolutely mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used car market. The exterior is flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections of any kind. The interior is equally pristine, showing virtually no signs of wear on the seats, dashboard, carpeting, or trim. Mechanically, this car is in excellent shape: the engine runs smoothly, all systems function perfectly, and there are no known issues whatsoever. Every component, from the electronics to the suspension, performs as it should. This is truly a turn-key vehicle that a buyer can drive away with complete confidence \u2014 no repairs, no surprises, just a beautifully maintained car ready for its next owner.",
