    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare find alert! This stunning vehicle is in absolute mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! The exterior shines with a flawless, showroom-quality finish, free of any scratches, dents, or blemishes. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells brand new, with pristine upholstery and every feature working perfectly. Under the hood, this beauty runs like a dream \u2014 smooth, responsive, and ready to impress on every drive. If you've been searching for a vehicle that truly has it all, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to own something this special! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
