    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a solid, dependable used car purchase. The exterior shows the expected minor wear for a vehicle of its age \u2014 you may notice light surface scratches and small scuffs in places, but there are no major dents, rust, or significant paint damage. The interior is well-maintained with normal signs of use, including minor wear on high-contact surfaces like the steering wheel and seat bolsters, but no tears, stains, or broken components. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems are functioning as expected. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and routine maintenance has been kept up. This is an honest, everyday driver that will serve you well without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 34000.0,
